division of fire and building safety said the damage to the 
rack and the condition of the rack causes us to focus on the lift 
charge were concentrating on what happened to make the rack 
dislodge 
the lift charge is made up of black powder that is placed 
beneath the rocket it propels the rocket through a tube into the 
air paige said 
