its not for just the casual player maybe for people who are one 
step above that 
groups form and reform with different members in different 
spots all night long but the theme is always the same have fun 
and play that fastdrivin music 
its kind of like having a buffet of music walker said 
if you cant find something you like you have no business out 
there but if you like bluegrass youll find plenty to like 
