programs must be conducted in conjunction with a stateapproved 
college or university teacher education program 
every candidate should have at least a bachelors degree 
candidates must receive substantial training in how to teach 
before beginning classroom work 
candidates working in the classroom must be supervised by a 
fullylicensed trained mentor and be evaluated frequently 
to become fully licensed the candidate must meet the same 
state requirements as those required of traditionalroute teachers 
