them as a symbol of counterproductive costcutting 
you did all that your nation had a right to expect but you 
were the victims of those who believed there was little need for 
trained and ready military forces in peacetime he said 
the army is ready to cut back he said 
but precipitous cuts of more than about 35000 active soldiers 
in any single year will fracture the combat capability that may be 
required to defend our nations vital interests vuono added 
martin said he agrees 
the moral of task force smith he said is never again send 
people into combat illprepared and without proper weapons 
