truce village of panmunjom inside the demilitarized zone dmz will 
be opened aug 15 to allow free travel between the two koreas 
it was not immediately clear whether both north and south 
koreans or foreigners would be permitted to freely cross the 
border in addition south korea also controls any passage through 
the heavily guarded border 
