only its sector of panmunjom which is very small said a senior 
seoul govenment official who spoke on condition of anonymity 
panmunjom is an ovalshaped joint security area straddling a 
portion of the 155mile border between the two koreas it is where 
military officials of both sides irregularly meet to discuss 
alleged armistice violations 
the north korean action would affect about 800 yards of the 
border 
