talks july 26 
it would be the first meeting between top officials of the two 
koreas since the divison of their peninsula in 1945 the korean 
border is tightly sealed and no one can cross the border without 
government approval which is rarely given 
the date announced for the border opening aug 15 is symbolic 
to both koreas on aug 15 1945 korea was liberated from japan 
