mitch snyder who was found hanged in the 
shelter he founded was eulogized today as a man of justice who 
answered a moral call to help the nations homeless 
snyder 46 was discovered dead thursday afternoon in a 
1400bed homeless shelter in a ragged neighborhood a few blocks 
