in protest the coalition on homelessness said it plans to 
flood the system bringing in homeless people from other areas 
to the civic center to overwhelm the new shelters said a group 
leader josh brandon 
the citys plan unfairly targets the homeless at the civic 
center while others throughout the city desire shelter as well he 
said 
we simply want to give people who want to get off the streets 
the opportunity to get off the streets brandon said 
