tactical questions is how to lay a claim to some of the partys 
vast holdings of newspapers the best buildings in cities all 
around the country a huge fleet of cars and bank accounts 
yeltsin warned that soviet communists are blindly following 
their eastern european comrades down the road to oblivion 
if you think there is a different possibility look at the 
fate of the communist parties of eastern europe they separated 
themselves from the people didnt understand their role and were 
left on the side of the road he said 
the only way out he said is for the communist party to fully 
accept all the trappings of the multiparty system that party 
leaders endorsed earlier this year 
yeltsin read rapidly and with little emotion from a prepared 
text more than 4600 delegates in the congress hall listened 
