out blaming gorbachev for letting the reins slip from his grasp 
for allowing the country to be plunged into chaos and anarchy and 
for the collapse of socialist ideals he said 
deep in their minds however theyre thinking how to return 
to the iron fist regular columns and uniformity he charged 
