<TEXT>
the nato leaders endorsed an historic change in policy by 
pledging to use nuclear weapons only as a last resort rather 
than maintaining uncertainty over when the arms would be deployed 
the change is designed to reassure the soviet union that the 
western alliance is not a poised military threat 
