our own western hemisphere and yet youre seeing now the 
emergence of democracies and youre seeing the emergence of free 
people there so its fundamental that people want democracy and 
freedom but i think natos major contribution has been to keeping 
the peace and yet its set an example that i think many in 
eastern europe now want to follow 
yes 
