2yearold son robyn by relying solely on prayer to heal the boy 
robyn died april 8 1986 and an autopsy showed he suffered from a 
congenital defect that had caused a bowel obstruction 
on friday hamlin placed the twitchells who faced up to 20 
years in prison on 10 years probation and said that they must 
take their three children to periodic health checkups under 
guidelines for children set by the american medical association 
