<TEXT>
kailuakona hawaii ap us rep joe kennedy dived into 
sharkfilled waters to help rescue a couple whose boat overturned 
in a tussle with a 485pound marlin according to kennedy and the 
skipper of his charter boat 
the massachusetts democrat on vacation with his twin 9yearold 
sons joseph jr and matthew was taking part in a fishing 
tournament sunday along with us rep bart gordon dtenn 
football player colin scott and exwashington redskin player john 
wilbur 
the crew of kennedys boat heard a distress call on the crafts 
radio sunday when the charter was about three miles off 
kailuakona on the west side of hawaii island said chuck harlan 
captain of the charter boat kealia 
the woman said their boat was sinking and she gave four 
different locations harland said in a telephone interview 
wednesday we saw lights out in the water and continued trolling 
in that direction 
when they got close they could see a man and a woman hanging 
onto an overturned fishing boat harlan said 
kennedy and others on the charter leapt in the water to save the 
couple harlan and kennedy said joe colin and my son mike 
jumped in and swam over to the boat harlan said 
i dont know if we got many points for intelligence kennedy 
told the boston herald in a telephone interview thursday it was 
tiger shark city 
she was really scared at that point kennedy said colin 
and i grabbed her and swam back to the boat 
the herald reported the rescued woman was mildred akaka the 
niece of us sen daniel akaka dhawaii akaka told the 
associated press earlier in the week that he hadnt heard about the 
incident 
after the rescue harlan said he saw a large marlin jump off to 
the north diving under the capsized boat he grabbed the vessels 
fishing pole still hooked to the marlin which apparently had sunk 
the couples boat in the first place 
the rescued woman worked the fish a while then turned the pole 
over to wilbur who eventually landed the 485pound marlin harlan 
said 
kennedy said a bleeding 300pound marlin the couple had caught 
earlier in the day probably attracted the sharks 
when he spotted the dead fish under the boat it kind of 
nearly gave me heart failure kennedy said 
kennedy 37 said of the incident it was classic old man and 
the sea stuff 
kennedy is the eldest son of the late sen robert kennedy since 
1987 he has represented the same district that his uncle john 
kennedy served before becoming senator and later president 
john kennedy gained fame during world war ii for his role in 
command of patroltorpedo boat pt109 in the solomon islands after 
the boat was rammed by a japanese warship kennedy towed a badly 
wounded soldier to safety american forces later rescued the crew 
