fourday convention won passage because it established standards 
like mandatory bachelors degrees supervision by certified 
teachers and enrollment in teacher accreditation courses officials 
said 
im not in favor of blanket alternative certification said 
rosanne bacon president of the massachusetts teachers association 
a former opponent of such teacher recruitment efforts 
